    <item>
      <title>英国资产管理公司正在竞相修复 ISA 股票菜单错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/uk-asset-managers-are-racing-to-fix-isa-stock-menu-errors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从 AJ Bell Plc 到 Fidelity International 等英国投资平台都在忙着修复一个错误，该错误允许客户在其免税账户上交易一些不合格的股票，而客户担心潜在的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/uk-asset-managers-are-racing-to-fix-isa-stock-menu-errors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国零售数据公布后欧洲股指期货下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股指期货表明，由于中国股市因令人失望的零售数据而下跌，该地区股市开盘可能走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弹劾案解除时间短暂，韩元和股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈遭弹劾后出现的反弹在周一被证明是短暂的，随着人们的注意力迅速从政治转移到经济，股市和货币逆转了早盘的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
